    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Rip the <strong>green leaves</strong> from your<strong> pak choi</strong> and set them aside</p><p>Chop the <strong>white bases</strong> into rough, large pieces</p><p>Discard the tough stalks</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
