    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, drain your <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped white pak choi bases</strong> and cook for a further 30 secs</p>",
