    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the<strong> peanut butter </strong>with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span><strong> boiled water</strong> in a small bowl give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add your<strong> soy sauce</strong> and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and mix until a smooth sauce remains – this is your <strong>bang bang dressing</strong></p><p>Tip: Use a small whisk to mix it well!</p>",
      "order": 6,
