    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rip the <strong>pak choi leaves</strong> into the pan and cook for 2 min further or until wilted</p><p>Add your <strong>sesame noodles</strong> and toss it all together – this is your<strong> king prawn stir-fry</strong></p><p>Note: Please make sure you cook your prawns thoroughly (until piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
