      "instruction": "<p>Set the<strong> king prawn stir-fry</strong> in the centre of the table, ready to share</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>bang bang dressing</strong> all over, garnish with the <strong>roasted peanuts </strong>and let everyone dig in</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
